column5: Would like to chat if any of you are Moose hunting in WMU 16 b this year. Thank you.
You may want to post it in the big game message board
Good thought northerneyes, I will post in big game also. Many on "Canada Eh" fish WMU 16b (St. Raphael Lake Provincial Park-Lake St. Joe area), thought some might hunt moose there also.
